  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Looking for a fresh start in your career?</strong><br>\nWhether you’re a fresh graduate, recently ORD, or exploring a new path, this Sales Consultant opportunity might be exactly what you’re looking for.</p>\n<p>We welcome individuals with <strong>no prior experience</strong>. You’ll receive full training, hands-on guidance, and the support you need to grow into a confident and capable sales professional.</p>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Engaging with customers through events, roadshows, and business campaigns</li>\n  <li>Presenting products and services confidently in face-to-face settings</li>\n  <li>Building meaningful relationships and understanding client needs</li>\n  <li>Working closely with a positive and motivated team</li>\n  <li>Learning effective communication, sales techniques, and people skills through regular training sessions</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Weekly payout with uncapped commissions</li>\n  <li>Performance-based bonuses for strong achievers</li>\n  <li>Workshops to help you improve, grow, and step into leadership roles</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to travel for work exposure and learning</li>\n  <li>A supportive environment where your effort is recognised</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Why This Role?</strong></h3>\n<p>You’ll gain valuable real-world experience, build confidence in communication, and develop practical skills that will benefit you in any future career path. If you’re driven, motivated, and enjoy talking to people, this role gives you the perfect platform to grow quickly.</p>\n<h3><strong>Ready to Get Started?</strong></h3>\n<p>If you’re excited to learn, grow, and build a career with plenty of opportunities, reach out and apply today. Positions are limited, and early applicants will be prioritised.</p>",
